snippet.title: Silent Rain - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Silent Rain will be available on October 20th 2023 on Steam. A demo is already available!

Silent Rain is a challenging hide & seek co-op horror game where each try, and death, will give you knowledge to go further on your next attempt.

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1791910/Silent_Rain/
Join our discord: https://discord.gg/aP5XnXVuGP
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/SeedlersInt
